    "name": "Monsterful Tavern",
    "steam_appid": 3230350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/2a0b72534f7131603d552029f0225ac3.webp?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/8f893ad6886cbec01f37184d7a00f0db.poster.avif?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/8f893ad6886cbec01f37184d7a00f0db.webm?t=1771599808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the owner of a tavern for monsters in a simulation RPG game infused with absurd black humor and real stories drawn from over a decade of experience running a board game bar. In Monsterful Tavern, you can cook knights, serve Whiskey on the Balls, upgrade your venue, and explore underground dungeons in search of the finest ingredients. The tavern is not just a kitchen and bar; it also features an underground farm, a barn, a slaughterhouse, and even a breeding ground for carnivorous bees!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/e922edf44aebe276733aacea00d5e732.webp?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/4c32ea8ba9b9491d6df17bdf133367e6.poster.avif?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/4c32ea8ba9b9491d6df17bdf133367e6.webm?t=1771599808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook a Bughetti and mix a Bloody Martini to satisfy your monster guests. You will get to squeeze out beetle juice, chop up magic mushrooms and fry the tastiest parts of knight in immersive minigames that will make you experience the monsterful tavern as if you were actually there!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/c5a880a96c00fbfe07afd53775c5ed93.webp?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/582784840ee6cd8ae71c9ada0a5cdf3e.poster.avif?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/582784840ee6cd8ae71c9ada0a5cdf3e.webm?t=1771599808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the prepared drinks and dishes to feed your guests in an immersive gameplay inspired by turn-based RPGs. Serve orcs, trolls, vampires and other monsters, with their individual tastes and quirks of character, which have a direct impact on gameplay. If you do well, your pouch will overflow with eyes – the currency of Undernests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/f37f449684a7cc6451d71d6d4c2bf971.webp?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/76d968f2d286af1f236efe98f816e87b.poster.avif?t=1771599808\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230350/extras/76d968f2d286af1f236efe98f816e87b.webm?t=1771599808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Undernests, an underground city located among stalagnate constellations, constantly plagued by knights' raids. Meet its unique inhabitants, visit the goblin workshop, pray at the Temple of the Big Round Troll, spend a night at the house of ill repute owned by Lady Grey, the vampire, and play a &quot;Castles&amp;Knights&quot; RPG campaign with your old friend. Your actions will leave a lasting impact on Undernests, but will it be for the better?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>     <br>     </p>",
